<text label="T1" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Based on the way you ranked the pools, these will be the pairings in the semifinals. Medal semifinals determine who plays in the championship game; classification semifinals determine who plays for 5th place.Choose a winner in each game:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions></paragraph></text>
